Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喜歡隊長？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫財前敏夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你喜歡上了隊長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:02:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少每個聽你講完的人 都對你沒話說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對 她們只是聽到我突然的告白嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是真對你沒話說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你指的藤堂吟隊長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}漂亮聰明又意志堅定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎麼看都沒希望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太沒禮貌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喜歡誰是人的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我從以前就很欣賞她那樣堅強的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總覺得有種…有安全感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還是去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你剛剛說什麼 冷冷地說了很惡毒的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉啊 你以前自己也說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要把戀愛帶到船上來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我才忍到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是已經忍不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真想揍你一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你已經…動手…了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你為什麼要找我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我聽說高中女生裡 有隊長的老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想來打探一下情報的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是報瀨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼時候認識的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第一次見到隊長是十多年前了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有沒有那時候的照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夠了 禁止你接近她們5公尺以內
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這什麼時候定的禁令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但她只是我媽媽的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒有跟她說過多少話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊 那我該怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以你能不能死了這條心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}敏夫你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想到了 把隊員的愛情長跑寫進我們的報導
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定會轟動的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報導？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我懂了 這是個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是個從未注意過的視角
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會太低俗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}挺好的 最近才被人說我們的報導播放數下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家會來看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定會的肯定會的 大家都喜歡這一套
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是說 我和隊長的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會透過網路全世界播出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 財前先生請你回自己房間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們自己拍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是說你礙事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:03.92,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康采風體W3\bord0\fs40\1c&HBF9AC9&\frx356\fry0\frz6.274\pos(456,60)}企鵝牧場送來的禮物{\fsp-25\i1}！！{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:03.92,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康中特圓體\bord5\3c&HBADDD7&\fs50\frz5.136\pos(634,238)\frx346\fry356}霜淇淋日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:03.92,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康中特圓體\bord3\b0\1c&H80B8DD&\3c&H4A5150&\fs50\frz5.136\pos(634,238)\frx346\fry356}霜淇淋日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:03.92,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@華康少女文字W5\bord0\fs30\1c&HA0CFCE&\pos(898,390)\frz285.5}來吃霜淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是什麼樣的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 隊長的性格啊男性關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛剛都說了 她只是我媽的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我又不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒怎麼跟她聊過天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去買點高麗菜 幫我顧一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 那我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來 找零
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來 您的找零
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能把錢給不認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很正經？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我感覺跟正經有點差別
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她的戀愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我哪知道 那時候我還在上幼稚園
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能當面問她了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當面？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是請她接受採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聊著聊著轉個彎把問題拋出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像藝人開記者會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}交往順利嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼要問我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 誰去採訪問問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前好像也發生過類似的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼不願意 出發前晚在甲板上聊過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們看見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你以為我們沒看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看你們關係挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那只是偶然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道你們關係不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不是不好吧 怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有距離啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但你們在甲板上聊過天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你都看見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看你們關係挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那只是偶然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們本來就都不擅長說話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以貴子一離開 我們就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}企鵝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒有孩子 不知道該跟她聊什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再說了 貴子實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真的不想跟她聊聊貴子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那孩子總是說 媽媽在等她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搜索中止了 是我做的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓你們久等了 請進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉提了個不情之請
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}佳苗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 報瀨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她還有點別的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}攝影機就位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 你們打算問什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天想採訪一下隊長的私生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喜歡的食物 日常生活等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有戀愛之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是你喜歡什麼樣的男性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不會回答和南極觀測無關的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小吟 人家高中生在問你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請說說看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近播放數下滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的很重要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}耳朵好紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不紅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隊長 您剛洗完澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喜歡什麼入浴劑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老實說 喜歡什麼類型？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}眼睛再大一點會不會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保持原樣就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}據說已經進入南極圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太陽不會沉下去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像雲一樣的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道 但她就是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算說是雲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}高雲 中雲 低雲也各有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無聊透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好大的雲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雲可真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明抓不到 但抬個頭就能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我哪懂那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我還是能意會一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼回事 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}採訪結果如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}佳苗這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟她沒關係 是我想問的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道隊長和小淵澤的女兒關係還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是出於好奇而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那孩子沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概是還沒有原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那可是個大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是隊長 有義務跟隊員溝通確認的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:24.84,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天〇八〇〇至一二〇〇允許艦上運動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.40,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺超痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冬天運動經常會這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}企鵝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你懂了嗎 像雲一樣是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多多少少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的 什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快告訴我啊 到底是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難以 言傳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子 你是故意讓我和那孩子獨處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對啊 因為那孩子需要小吟的靈魂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是你的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}噓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想聽聽你是怎麼看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想聽我說恨你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從媽媽登上民間觀測船開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就問了她很多遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟她說南極觀測還有很多危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是你還是要去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道南極是個什麼樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我那時是隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你犯了什麼錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是判斷失誤 才把我媽媽留在南極的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當時別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了 最後讓我問一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是真心的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真心這麼想的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我才討厭談這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我根本不知道自己是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是…只是媽媽沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我每天的生活並沒有變化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和等她回來的每一天完全一樣 什麼都沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我日日夜夜都在想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彷彿自己還在等媽媽回來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想要改變這種生活 我就得出發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去那片 比宇宙還要遙遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兩舷慢速後退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兩舷慢速後退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}撞上固定冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要衝過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是要開到冰上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯 要先大幅度後退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兩舷停止 兩舷慢速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兩舷停止 兩舷慢速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}衝進冰層裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用船體的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}破壞冰層
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才叫破冰船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果冰層沒碎怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就一直重複
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重複到冰層破碎為止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到南極真的好艱難
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤其這一帶是出了名的難靠岸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼偏偏要挑這個地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為只有這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極觀測正規化 是在第二次世界大戰後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道這些嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戰敗國的日本想派遣觀測隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多國家都對此不信任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再加上日本沒什麼發言權
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後被分到的地區
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是被公認為不可能靠岸的東翁古爾島這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是被刁難了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道有沒有被刁難
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過可能拐彎抹角地包含了這層意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就好像在說「日本人 你們有本事就來啊」似的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:15:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽起來真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過大家聽了都熱血起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全日本募款資助計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}造船工人們嘔心瀝血造出了觀測船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一次一次又一次 絕不言棄奮力拚搏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像破開冰層一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一步又一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一次又一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第二強速
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}衝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}衝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:16:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還沒 還早著呢 得一直到我們抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一年又一年 無論多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一次又一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子 貴子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 小淵澤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:31.01,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是…美極了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:06.07,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そっと記した夢　言い訳ばかりして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:16.80,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ほったらかしにしていた　叶うのが怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:25.57,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何があるのかも　何が変わるのかも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:30.86,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}行ってみなきゃ分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:38.97,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあ　一歩前に　踏み出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:45.40,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大きな夢を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:49.86,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハルカ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:54.44,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真っ白な世界に　残したいな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:59.40,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}最初の足跡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:09.05,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界の最果てで　転がっていく太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:14.96,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}南風はやがて島を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:19.30,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}髪を揺らす
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:30.66,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}小さな夢を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:35.40,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}願えた　ツヨクツヨク
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:37.97,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}履き慣れたスニーカー
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:44.65,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}紐をギュッと締め直して
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:50.10,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}でかい夢を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:54.57,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハルカ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:59.26,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}波に揺られてかたふりして
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:04.19,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}進んでいくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:08.68,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}宇宙より遠くへ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:06.07,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}偷偷記下了夢想 卻只找了一堆藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:16.80,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想到自己總是忘記夢想 就怕去實現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:25.57,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}怕出什麼事 怕有什麼變故
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:30.86,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}但駐足不前 就什麼都明白不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:38.97,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向前一步 邁出勇敢的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:45.40,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想實現心底大大的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:49.86,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遙遠不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:54.44,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想在那一片純白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:59.40,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}留下我最初的腳印
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:09.05,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}紅紅的一輪夕陽 沉入了世界的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:14.96,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}海面南風跨越萬千島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:19.30,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}吹動起我的髮梢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:30.66,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想實現心底小小的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:35.40,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}用力再用力 向神明許願
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:37.97,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}穿上熟悉的運動鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:44.65,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}緊緊地繫好鞋帶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:50.10,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想實現心底大大的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:54.57,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遙遠不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:59.26,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就在波濤之中舉杯高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:04.19,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}繼續一步步前進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:08.68,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}去比宇宙更遙遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我話說在前頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是真的真的真的 想為隊長做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是她完全沒有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隊員哪幫得了隊長 人家也不會讓你幫的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把你的心情 交給一個你碰得到人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弓子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對 沒有這回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我之前是怎麼塞進箱子裡的 好神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收拾好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 收拾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你能睜眼說瞎話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要出去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小結 帶上攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能下去感受一下 半徑5公尺以內
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明白 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨 你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終點！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是你媽媽來過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}羨慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}羨慕吧 嫉妒吧 恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你們趾高氣昂地嘲笑我 我也相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你們以不可能為由背叛我 我也沒有放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是結果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼樣 我到南極了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}羨慕吧！嫉妒吧！恨吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}活該！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就想說這些？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.81,0:21:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}壓抑了很久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什麼關係 這才是報瀨嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}活該
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}活該
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2 活該
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2 活該
Comment: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:24.85,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}長いトンネルの出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:35.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:41.39,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}間違っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:52.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　僕は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:23:03.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}汚れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:14.36,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言葉も　きっと見つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:19.98,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:25.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:24.85,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}尋找著漫長隧道的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:35.77,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}向著泛著微光氣味的方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:41.39,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}就算走錯了 也別忘了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:52.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}從這裡開始 我將踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:23:03.09,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}緊緊捏住手心裡 髒髒的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:14.36,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}沒說出口的話 我也一定會找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:19.98,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}隨你們嘲笑吧 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:25.31,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要相信自己 邁出腳步
